#'   \href{https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/22867780}{PubMed}
#'
#' \href{https://euroqol.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/EQ-5D-5L_Crosswalk_Index_Value_Calculator_v2.xls}{EQ-5D-5L Crosswalk Index Value Calculator}
